manage-mods <instance> <action>
  create cfg/instance.cfg if it doesn't exist

Actions:

update
  update all mods

config
  directory <valid path>
    path to mods dir
    overwrite any existing entry
    fail if parent dir doesn't exist
    create target dir if doesn't exist

  mcversion <valid version>
    supported minecraft version
    overwrite any existing entry
    must be a valid version

  channels [add|remove] [valid channels]
    add list of channels
    remove list of channels
    space separated list of paths

  include [add|remove] [valid paths to config files to include]
    add list of paths
    remove list of paths
    space separated list of paths of config files to include

mod
  add modname
  remove modname
  update modname
  freeze modname

* TODO
* support adding specific version of mod
